HEADWORD: Laura
<hw>Lau"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL., fr. Gr. (<?/)
lane, defile, also, a kind of monastery.]</ety> <fld>(R. C. Ch.)</fld>
